OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start with some drizzly
OL,6,Foutbreaks at first. Turning drier as
OL,7,Fthe day goes on, perhaps with some
OL,8,Fbrighter spells at times. However,
OL,9,Fstaying mostly cloudy through the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud lingers at first with
OL,12,Fsome showers in the south. Clearer
OL,13,Fspells will develop through the night.
OL,14,FStaying dry and fairly mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FDry on Tuesday but largely
OL,17,Fcloudy. A few brighter spells are
OL,18,Fpossible at times. Temperatures around
OL,19,Faverage for the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
